725957f-a.title: Queens: 165th Street - Jamaica Avenue
725957f-a.text:
165th Street, east side, between Janaica Avenue and 94th
Avenue, viewing south from near the forner toward the Long
Island Railroad tracks and showing typical homes of old Jamaica.
165th Street, here, was formerly called Puntine Street.
P. L. Sperr  April 7, 1932
